
Requires:
 - valac
 - g-ir-compiler
 - python
 - libgee >= 0.8

To test bindings:
$ make clean && make
$ sh run.sh

To run unit tests:
$ make clean && make debug
$ ./debug/libvoxel_test

If tests fail, you can step through with a debugger like so:
$ cd debug
$ nemiver libvoxel_test


For more information on using vala bindings with other languages, check out: https://github.com/antono/vala-object